ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d30113ef78940e9c99855d7093cc3eac657ff86","tid":489572,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>扑野都冇地方<br />\n有地方既又冇時間（用晒黎返工）<br />\n<br />\n要提高生育率 早放一個鐘已經搞掂</blockquote><br />\n你講到d人<br />\n唔生仔<br />\n係因為無時間同地方扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高收入家庭先唔生"},{"pid":"aed03deb0091f40c112271e195b23d13abf19174","tid":489572,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新加坡是吃子的社會，有錢也想生吧</blockquote><br />\n新加坡只有<span style=\"color: red;\">大學生同精英</span>先可以生育，呢個係國父李光耀制定的規矩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n愛國的內在<br />\n赴歐美的內心"}]}